des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your Homvana humidifiers and air purifiers. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our Homvana app in the app market, then register an account;
(2) Configure your devices in our Homvana app and change appropriate names for your devices;
(3) Enable Homvana skill, and you'll be navigated to the Homvana login page;
(4) Follow the instructions on the page to complete the linking;
(5) Now, all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
"Alexa, turn on the humidifier."
"Alexa, turn off the air purifier."
"Alexa, set the humidifier warm mist to high."
"Alexa, set the air purifier to sleep mode."
